80 22 88</a></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-white p-2\" aria-label=\"Открыть меню\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-navigation\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main-content\" class=\"pt-20\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Welcome Pack: HR uchun to'liq gid (tarkib, byudjet)\",\"description\":\"Welcome packni to'g'ri tuzing: 3 daraja tarkib, byudjet formulasi, 5 xato. Toshkentda buyurtma qiling!\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/welcome-pack-hr-uchun-toliq-gid\",\"image\":\"/images/blog/welcome-pack-hr-uchun-toliq-gid.jpg\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-03-03\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-03-03\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/logo192.png\"}},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/welcome-pack-hr-uchun-toliq-gid\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Welcome Pack: HR uchun to'liq gid (tarkib, byudjet)\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/welcome-pack-hr-uchun-toliq-gid\"}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-8\"><ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-400 flex-wrap gap-y-1\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz\">Graver.uz</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 truncate max-w-xs\">Welcome Pack: HR uchun to&#x27;liq gid (tarkib, byudjet)</li></ol></nav><header class=\"mb-10\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight\">Welcome Pack: HR uchun to&#x27;liq gid (tarkib, byudjet)</h1><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-500\"><time dateTime=\"2026-03-03\">2-mart, 2026</time><span>2<!-- --> <!-- -->daqiqa o&#x27;qish</span><span>Graver.uz</span></div></header><div class=\"mb-10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/blog/welcome-pack-hr-uchun-toliq-gid.jpg\" alt=\"Welcome Pack: HR uchun to&#x27;liq gid (tarkib, byudjet)\" class=\"w-full aspect-video object-cover\" loading=\"eager\"/></div><article class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p>Welcome pack - bu shunchaki &quot;sovg&#x27;a quti&quot; emas: u onboardingni tezlashtiradi, brendni his qildiradi va xodimga foydali narsalar beradi. Ushbu gid HR uchun: tarkib, byudjet, xatolar va Toshkentda buyurtma qilish yo&#x27;li.</p>\n<h2>Welcome pack nima uchun kerak: biznes foydasi</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Moslashuv tezlashadi: yangi xodim &quot;nima qayerda?&quot; deb kamroq chalg&#x27;iydi</li>\n<li>Loyallik ortadi: &quot;men qadrlanaman&quot; signali</li>\n<li>Brend intizomi: bir xil standart, bir xil vizual kod</li>\n<li>Ichki kommunikatsiya: unboxing postlari, jamoa ichida ijobiy kontent</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Tarkibni qanday tanlash: 3 daraja (bazaviy-standart-premium)</h2>\n<h3>Bazaviy (amaliy minimum)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Daftar + ruchka (gravirovka)</li>\n<li>Lanyard/badge-holder</li>\n<li>Stikerlar + tabrik karta</li>\n<li>Qadoqlash (oddiy, ammo chiroyli)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Standart (eng ko&#x27;p tanlanadigan)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Termo-krujka yoki suv idishi (lazer gravirovka)</li>\n<li>Kabel/adapter, kichik organayzer</li>\n<li>Mini-souvenir: metal brelok (gravirovka)</li>\n<li>Brend quti + ichki dizayn</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Premium (top rol va VIP onboarding)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Soat yoki premium ruchka (gravirovka)</li>\n<li>Zaryadlovchi (powerbank) yoki aksessuarlar to&#x27;plami</li>\n<li>Yog&#x27;och/plastik stendlar (desk set)</li>\n<li>Personal message + nomli qadoqlash</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Byudjetni hisoblash: oddiy formula</h2>\n<p>Amaliy formula: (buyumlar qiymati + gravirovka/print + qadoqlash + komplektatsiya + logistika) × zaxira koeffitsienti.</p>\n<p>Zaxira koeffitsienti odatda 1.05-1.15: yo&#x27;qotish, qayta gravirovka yoki qo&#x27;shimcha xodimlar uchun.</p>\n<p>Agar jamoa tez o&#x27;sayotgan bo&#x27;lsa, &quot;stock&quot; qilish (10-20% zaxira) onboardingni soddalashtiradi.</p>\n<h2>Lazer gravirovka: nima uchun aynan u</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Chidamlilik: yozuv o&#x27;chmaydi, ayniqsa metall/yog&#x27;ochda</li>\n<li>Premium ko&#x27;rinish: &quot;print&quot;dan ko&#x27;ra aniqroq va toza</li>\n<li>Shaxsiylashtirish: ism, lavozim, qisqa shior, QR-kod</li>\n<li>Katta tirajlarda ham bir xil sifat</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>5 tipik xato (va qanday tuzatish)</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Faqat &quot;chiroy&quot;ga ishlash</strong>&gt;Foydasi yo&#x27;q buyumlar tezda chetga chiqadi. Har pozitsiyada &quot;ishdagi value&quot; bo&#x27;lsin.</li>\n<li><strong>Haddan tashqari aralash brending</strong>&gt;Katta logo hamma joyda - arzon ko&#x27;rinadi. Minimal, aniq gravirovka yetarli.</li>\n<li><strong>Rolga moslashtirmaslik</strong>&gt;Hamma uchun bir xil - ba&#x27;zi rollar uchun keraksiz. 2-3 segment yetarli.</li>\n<li><strong>Muddatni noto&#x27;g&#x27;ri rejalash</strong>&gt;Tadbir/ish boshlash sanasidan kamida 10-14 kun oldin start qiling (tiraj katta bo&#x27;lsa - 3 hafta).</li>\n<li><strong>Ro&#x27;yxat va transliteratsiya nazoratsiz</strong>&gt;Ism-xatolar brendga zarba. Excel ro&#x27;yxat + ikki bosqichli tekshiruv qiling.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Toshkentda qanday buyurtma beriladi: qisqa yo&#x27;l xaritasi</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Brif: xodimlar soni, rollar, byudjet, deadline</li>\n<li>Maket: logo/ism formatlari, qadoqlash dizayni</li>\n<li>Namuna: 1-2 dona test</li>\n<li>Ishlab chiqarish: lazer gravirovka + komplektatsiya</li>\n<li>QC + yetkazib berish: ofisga yoki tadbir joyiga</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Buyurtma bermoqchimisiz?</strong> Telegram <a href=\"https://t.me/graveruz\">@graveruz</a> ga yozing yoki saytdagi shaklni to&#x27;ldiring.</p></article><section class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">O&#x27;xshash maqolalar</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/keys-welcome-pack-povysil-enps-v-it-kompanii-uz\">Keys: Welcome Pack eNPSni 23% oshirdi - Toshkent</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Welcome pack natijalari: eNPS +23%. Tarkib, jarayon va HR fikri. Hisob-kitob so&#x27;rang!</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/it-kompaniyalar-uchun-merch-toshkent\">IT-kompaniyalar uchun merch Toshkentda</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Toshkentdagi IT-kompaniyalar uchun premium merch: xudi, powerbank, welcome pack va lazerli gravyura. Ishlab chiqarishdan oldin maket.</p></article></div></section><div class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8\"><a class=\"text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-400 transition flex items-center\" href=\"/uz/blog\">← <!-- -->Blogga qaytish</a></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-black border-t border-gray-800 mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\" href=\"/uz\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold\">G</span></div><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Graver<span class=\"text-teal-500\">.uz</span></span></a><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">Toshkentda biznes uchun premium lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik va brendlash</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">Navigatsiya</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz#services\">Xizmatlar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/catalog-products\">Mahsulotlar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/contacts\">Aloqa</a></li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">Aloqa</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a href=\"tel:+998770802288\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">+998 77 080 22 88</a></li><li><a href=\"tel:+998974802288\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">+998 97 480 22 88</a></li><li><a href=\"https://t.me/GraverAdm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">Telegram</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm\">Toshkent, Mukimiy ko&#x27;chasi</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-gray-800 mt-8 pt-8 text-center\"><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Graver.uz. <!-- -->Barcha huquqlar himoyalangan<!-- -->.</p></div></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-68f22649503f8e75.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"