od\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Ichki kommunikatsiya: unboxing postlari, jamoa ichida ijobiy kontent\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Tarkibni qanday tanlash: 3 daraja (bazaviy-standart-premium)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Bazaviy (amaliy minimum)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Daftar + ruchka (gravirovka)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Lanyard/badge-holder\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Stikerlar + tabrik karta\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Qadoqlash (oddiy, ammo chiroyli)\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Standart (eng ko'p tanlanadigan)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Termo-krujka yoki suv idishi (lazer gravirovka)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Kabel/adapter, kichik organayzer\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Mini-souvenir: metal brelok (gravirovka)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Brend quti + ichki dizayn\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Premium (top rol va VIP onboarding)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Soat yoki premium ruchka (gravirovka)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Zaryadlovchi (powerbank) yoki aksessuarlar to'plami\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Yog'och/plastik stendlar (desk set)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Personal message + nomli qadoqlash\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Byudjetni hisoblash: oddiy formula\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Amaliy formula: (buyumlar qiymati + gravirovka/print + qadoqlash + komplektatsiya + logistika) × zaxira koeffitsienti.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Zaxira koeffitsienti odatda 1.05-1.15: yo'qotish, qayta gravirovka yoki qo'shimcha xodimlar uchun.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Agar jamoa tez o'sayotgan bo'lsa, \\\"stock\\\" qilish (10-20% zaxira) onboardingni soddalashtiradi.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Lazer gravirovka: nima uchun aynan u\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Chidamlilik: yozuv o'chmaydi, ayniqsa metall/yog'ochda\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Premium ko'rinish: \\\"print\\\"dan ko'ra aniqroq va toza\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Shaxsiylashtirish: ism, lavozim, qisqa shior, QR-kod\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Katta tirajlarda ham bir xil sifat\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"5 tipik xato (va qanday tuzatish)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Faqat \\\"chiroy\\\"ga ishlash\"}],\">Foydasi yo'q buyumlar tezda chetga chiqadi. Har pozitsiyada \\\"ishdagi value\\\" bo'lsin.\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Haddan tashqari aralash brending\"}],\">Katta logo hamma joyda - arzon ko'rinadi. Minimal, aniq gravirovka yetarli.\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Rolga moslashtirmaslik\"}],\">Hamma uchun bir xil - ba'zi rollar uchun keraksiz. 2-3 segment yetarli.\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Muddatni noto'g'ri rejalash\"}],\">Tadbir/ish boshlash sanasidan kamida 10-14 kun oldin start qiling (tiraj katta bo'lsa - 3 hafta).\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Ro'yxat va transliteratsiya nazoratsiz\"}],\">Ism-xatolar brendga zarba. Excel ro'yxat + ikki bosqichli tekshiruv qiling.\"]}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Toshkentda qanday buyurtma beriladi: qisqa yo'l xaritasi\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Brif: xodimlar soni, rollar, byudjet, deadline\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Maket: logo/ism formatlari, qadoqlash dizayni\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Namuna: 1-2 dona test\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Ishlab chiqarish: lazer gravirovka + komplektatsiya\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"QC + yetkazib berish: ofisga yoki tadbir joyiga\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Buyurtma bermoqchimisiz?\"}],\" Telegram \",[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://t.me/graveruz\",\"children\":\"@graveruz\"}],\" ga yozing yoki saytdagi shaklni to'ldiring.\"]}]]\nb:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"name\":\"theme-color\",\"content\":\"#14b8a6\"}]]\n8:null\n9:null\nd:[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"Welcome Pack: HR uchun to'liq gid (tarkib, byudjet)\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"Welcome packni to'g'ri tuzing: 3 daraja tarkib, byudjet formulasi, 5 xato. Toshkentda buyurtma qiling!\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"2\",{\"rel\":\"canonical\",\"href\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/welcome-pack-hr-uchun-toliq-gid\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"3\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"ru\",\"href\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/ru/blog/welcome-pack-hr-uchun-toliq-gid\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"4\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"uz\",\"href\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/welcome-pack-hr-uchun-toliq-gid\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"5\",{\"rel\":\"alternate\",\"hrefLang\":\"x-default\",\"href\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/ru/blog/welcome-pack-hr-uchun-toliq-gid\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"6\",{\"property\":\"og:title\",\"content\":\"Welcome Pack: HR uchun to'liq gid (tarkib, byudjet)\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"7\",{\"property\":\"og:description\",\"content\":\"Welcome packni to'g'r